<div class="hero-unit container">
	<h1>Tumblr Stats</h1>
	<p>See what happens on your tumblog, whether you're blogging or sharing cat pictures.</p>
	<%= image_tag "dashboardlymac.png" %>
</div>

<div class="container marketing">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="span4">
			<%= image_tag 'track.svg', :width => 150 %>
			<h2>Track Variations</h2>
			<p>See how traffic, reblogs and more change. Hover over arrows to see percentage differences.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="span4">
			<%= image_tag 'dig.svg', :width => 150 %>
			<h2>Dig Deep</h2>
			<p>Mountain drills down and shows you how individual posts stack up against one another.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="span4">
			<%= image_tag 'cross.svg', :width => 150 %>
			<h2>Cross Metrics</h2>
			<p>Mountain pulls information from Tumblr, and Analytics to give  the most accurate information about your site.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

